Title: custom notes for host and services: Fix multiple note display and fix note search path for services
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1693229413
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0p33

This werk adds the hr tag to the list of allowed tags, solving the problem of showing multiple notes for a host or service in the gui.
It also fixes the problem that caused service notes stored in a path with a wildcard hostname to not be displayed.
